Call To Arms (Tsung Hua, 1972) CN, Remastered

Plot: The aggressive and dangerous Chin empire occupies the put-upon Chao kingdom while the hero-filled Wei empire is paralyzed by an indecisive ruler. Adventure, intrigue, death and tragedy reigns before the triumphant clash of the armies. 

Overview: Shen Chiang both wrote and directed this monumental tale of three entire kingdoms. The aggressive and dangerous Chin empire occupies the put-upon Chao kingdom while the hero-filled Wei empire is paralyzed by an indecisive ruler. Adventure, intrigue, death and tragedy reigns before the triumphant clash of the armies. Shen, scriptwriter of the landmark &quot;Temple Of The Red Lotus&quot;, presents it all with a sure touch and an eye for the spectacular. 

